    "If there were mindless responses, the distribution of responses would be more uniform.",
    "A noteworthy aspect of our study is that the text analysis was done automatically.",
    "Our observation is that the summaries and sentiment scores correspond to how we ourselves would summarize and rate the truck drivers' comments.",
